Package: beskid
Version: __VERSION__
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Piotr Mikstacki <piotr@beskid-lang.org>
Installed-Size: __INSTALLED_SIZE_KB__
Depends: libc6
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://beskid-lang.org
Description: Beskid compiler CLI and LSP (AOT, host composition)
 Beskid is an AOT-only compiler with host composition. This package ships the
 prebuilt beskid CLI and beskid_lsp binaries, installed to /usr/bin and placed
 on the system PATH automatically.
